      "rationale": "Primary QoI is the relative hemolysis index RH = NIH_device / NIH_predicate. This is the direct regulatory comparator for 510(k) substantial equivalence. Secondary QoIs (wall shear stress distribution, scalar stress exposure time) provide mechanistic traceability to the Giersiepen power-law hemolysis model."
